<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p> The burial  niche which is in the vault belongs to M(arcus) Aur(elius) Srep[anos] also known as Papias, having been granted [through the] Property-archive [by . . .  ] Tolmides in which [may be buried] whomever St[ephanos wishes]</p>
</div>
